trans-unit.source: Provides enumeration functionality for the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.

Gets the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object that represents the current cryptographic attribute in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.

Advances the enumeration to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.

`true` if the enumeration successfully moved to the next <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object; `false` if the enumerator is at the end of the enumeration.

Resets the enumeration to the first <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.

Gets the current <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object from the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.

A <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObject"></xref> object that represents the current cryptographic attribute in the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.CryptographicAttributeObjectCollection"></xref> collection.
